SECTION A: ACS758 CURRENT SENSOR
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

    Battery Output (0-30A)
    ─────────────┬─────────────
                 │
           ┌─────┴─────┐
           │  ACS758   │
           │  IC       │    Pins (SOIC-8):
        [+]│┌────────┐ │    1: IP+ (High current path +)
         ──┤│        │ │    2: GND
        [-]││ SOIC-8 │ │    3: IP- (High current path -)
         ──┤│        │ │    4: GND
           │└────────┘ │    5: VOUT (Signal output)
           │  [5]      │    6: GND
           │   ├─────[100nF]───GND
           │   │
           │   └─[10µF]───GND  (Bulk filter)
           │   │
           │   └─[To ADC pin 34]
           │
           ├─ +5V [from USB]
           │
           └─ GND
           
    At 0A:  VOUT = 2.5V
    At +15A: VOUT = 2.5V + (15 × 0.04) = 3.1V
    At +30A: VOUT = 2.5V + (30 × 0.04) = 3.7V
    At -30A: VOUT = 2.5V - (30 × 0.04) = 1.3V


SECTION B: VOLTAGE DIVIDER
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

    Boost Output (12-90V)
    ─────────────┬──────────────
                 │
              [R1]  1.7M Ω 1/2W
              (Metal film)
                 │
                 ├─ VOUT ──[100nF]──GND
                 │          ──[10µF]──GND
                 │          ──[1M pull-down]──GND
                 │
                 ├──────→ [To ADC pin 35]
                 │
              [R2]  100k Ω 1/4W
              (Metal film)
                 │
                GND


    Voltage divider calculation:
    ───────────────────────────
    VOUT = VIN × R2/(R1+R2)
    VOUT = VIN × 100k/(1700k+100k)
    VOUT = VIN / 18
    
    At 12V:  VOUT = 12/18 = 0.667V
    At 48V:  VOUT = 48/18 = 2.667V
    At 90V:  VOUT = 90/18 = 5.000V
    
    Perfect mapping to ADC (0-5V)!
    
    ⚠️  Important:
    - Use 1% tolerance resistors (metal film)
    - Place resistors close to ADC input
    - Add 100nF bypass cap right at ADC pin


SECTION C: DS18B20 TEMPERATURE SENSOR
═════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

    From Charger Heatsink / PCB
                 │
              (Sensor)
                 │
         ┌───────┼───────┐
         │       │       │
        GND     DATA    +3.3V
         │       │       │
         │       │     [+3.3V rail]
         │       │
         │      [R Pull-up]  4.7kΩ
         │       │
         │       └───────→ [GPIO 32 OneWire]
         │
        GND


    OneWire Protocol:
    ────────────────
    - Single wire data line
    - Open-drain with pull-up
    - Slave addresses unique per chip
    - Temperature resolution: 0.0625°C
    - Conversion time: ~750ms
    - Range: -55°C to +125°C


